Every Starfighter in Star Wars ExplainedLucasfilms' Doug Chiang and Amy Beth Christenson explain each and every type of starfighter from the Star Wars movie franchise.
These small, combat-focused spacecrafts have become a canvas for some of the most iconic designs in all of cinema.
Ever wondered why the "snout" of the X-Wing is so pronounced, or why the Y-Wing's paneling is so bare?
Amy Beth and Doug offer all these insights and much more!
Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker hits theaters December 20th